Reasoning: The paper discusses self-organizing particle systems and presents algorithms for leader election and shape formation, which are relevant topics in multi-agent systems (cs.MA) and robotics (cs.RO). The use of computational elements and the discussion of limitations also suggest a connection to distributed systems (cs.DS) and control systems (cs.SY). Finally, the mention of memory requirements and local-control algorithms may indicate a connection to computer architecture (cs.CC).
